Quickstrike:



"Ah reckon she will," he said, mentioning about KitKat. They had 
talked before, and they got along fine. She was a reasonable femm-
bot. And respected him as well.

He had a relaxed look in his eyes. He knew things were going to be 
fine. Without Megatron most of all. Things were better for him than 
the original Beast Wars. Things had settled down, he was no longer on 
the run, and other bots weren't snapping at him.
